



About:

  This application was created by Williams <wangshimeng@gmail.com>.

  Its an associated application of the WiFi Mouse app, which can turn your phone into a wireless mouse, 
keyboard, and remote desktop device (RDP), and also has functions such as media control, presentation control, and file browsing.
Download WiFi Mouse: 
  Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.necta.wifimousefree
  iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/id629552573

Build:

 sh builddep.sh
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=/usr ..
 cpack ..


Install:

 sudo make install

 run /usr/sbin/mouseserver

Or:

 Double click mouseserver.deb file and let system install it to /usr/bin/

Have fun!
